<!doctype html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
	<meta charset="utf-8" />
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1" />
	<title>Obrigado</title>
	<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.2/css/all.min.css">
	<style>
		:root {
    --primary: #5d46f4;
    --success: #10b981;
    --bg: #f8fafc;
    --text: #1e293b;
}

body { 
    font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, sans-serif; 
    margin: 0; 
    padding: 40px 20px; 
    color: var(--text); 
    background-color: var(--bg);
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
}

.success-icon {
    font-size: 3.5rem;
    color: var(--success);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    animation: scaleUp 0.5s ease-out;
}

@keyframes scaleUp {
    0% { transform: scale(0); }
    80% { transform: scale(1.1); }
    100% { transform: scale(1); }
}

h2.ok { 
    font-weight: 800; 
    color: #064e3b; 
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    text-align: center;
}

.card { 
    background: white;
    border: none;
    border-radius: 20px; 
    padding: 32px; 
    max-width: 550px; 
    width: 100%;
    box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
}

.instruction-text {
    color: #64748b;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    text-align: center;
}

label { font-weight: 600; display: block; margin-top: 12px; font-size: 14px; color: #475569; }

input[type="email"] { 
    width: 100%; 
    padding: 14px; 
    border: 2px solid #e2e8f0; 
    border-radius: 12px; 
    margin-top: 8px; 
    box-sizing: border-box;
    font-size: 16px;
    transition: 0.2s;
}

input:focus { outline: none; border-color: var(--primary); }

button { 
    width: 100%;
    background: var(--primary); 
    color: white; 
    padding: 14px; 
    border: 0; 
    border-radius: 12px; 
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: 16px;
    cursor: pointer; 
    margin-top: 20px; 
    transition: 0.3s;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 8px;
}

button:hover { background: #4a38c7; transform: translateY(-2px); }

.credentials-box {
    margin-top: 32px;
    background: #f1f5f9;
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 20px;
}

.credential-item {
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    padding: 12px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
}

.credential-item:last-child { border: none; }

.credential-item span:first-child {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: #64748b;
    font-weight: 600;
}

.credential-item strong {
    font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, monospace;
    color: var(--primary);
    background: #fff;
    padding: 4px 8px;
    border-radius: 6px;
    border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
}

.warning-box {
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #94a3b8;
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    gap: 6px;
}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="success-icon">
        <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i>
    </div>
    
    <h2 class="ok">Pagamento Confirmado!</h2>

    <div class="card">
        <p class="instruction-text">
            Sua compra foi processada com sucesso. Informe seu e-mail abaixo para liberar suas credenciais de acesso imediatamente.
        </p>


        <div class="credentials-box">
            <div style="font-weight: 800; font-size: 14px; margin-bottom: 15px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-key" style="color: var(--primary)"></i> Suas Credenciais
            </div>
            
            <div class="credential-item">
                <span>E-MAIL</span>
                <strong><%= email || 'Aguardando...' %></strong>
            </div>
            
            <div class="credential-item">
                <span>SENHA</span>
                <strong><%= password %></strong>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="warning-box">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-circle-info"></i>
            Você poderá alterar sua senha na área de membros.
        </div>
    </div>

    <div style="margin-top: 30px;">
        <a href="/membros" style="color: var(--primary); font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none;">
            Acessar Área de Membros <i class="fa-solid fa-up-right-from-square" style="font-size: 12px;"></i>
        </a>
    </div>
</body>	
</html>


